{"_id": "JdURFEMCHLfnMPMg", "name": "The Leacher's Emerald", "type": "loot", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Ancient relic imbued with necrotic energies by an evil necromancer. Once attuned, master can implant emerald into a living creature's chest (target resists with Grappling contest, PHB p.195). Bonus action: transfer 3d6 HP from victim to self (range 60ft). 2 charges/day, recharges at dawn. Master always knows direction and distance to emerald, and which plane it's on. Radiates evil; using for intended purpose shifts alignment one step toward evil.</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Area 24 - dropped by General Montarthas on death</p><p><strong>Rarity:</strong> Rare</p><p><em>Requires attunement.</em></p>"}, "quantity": 1, "weight": 0, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "attunement": 1, "equipped": false, "rarity": "rare", "identified": true}, "effects": [], "flags": {"questwright": {"id": "item_leachers_emerald", "location": "Area 24 - dropped by General Montarthas on death"}}}
{"_id": "clej6I62OA9vA7L4", "name": "Scroll of Invisibility", "type": "loot", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": {"value": "<p>Found on DC 10 Perception check. DC 10 Arcana confirms magical preservation.</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Area 10 - The Wizard's Bedroom</p><p><strong>Rarity:</strong> Uncommon</p>"}, "quantity": 1, "weight": 0, "price": {"value": 0, "denomination": "gp"}, "attunement": 0, "equipped": false, "rarity": "uncommon", "identified": true}, "effects": [], "flags": {"questwright": {"id": "item_scroll_invisibility", "location": "Area 10 - The Wizard's Bedroom"}}}
